</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-36_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-e80fc86b-0a02-46ba-9a50-e4a56314a8d6"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Learning and development professionals must collaborate with others to change the learning culture in organisations. They should focus on the following factors:
</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dhFVuh gFqzWs pf-39_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-40_">Questioning and influencing for improvement
