</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></details></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-101_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-102_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-103_">Conclusion</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-105_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-5654ebd1-7989-4aa9-a4e5-388a3fcdc28e"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">L&amp;D professionals are crucial in transforming organisational learning cultu<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span>res. They can drive a shift towards a more positive and inclusive learning culture.
